metadata.description:
Will the RP Sound Guardians encounter the Rillas? If we mint out, it's bound to happen.....

Once a song is minted out, all holders of that song will be given special privileges for the NFT EP release. These include:

- 5% primary royalties to be shared between the holders of the song.
- Free Mint/WL status for the drop in question.
- One RP Music Key ( https://app.niftykit.com/drops/rappackkeys )
- Discord role - RP Rilla received & will be pooled into weekly airdrops of Gorilla Styled/Musical theme art & Music NFTs.
- Token gated content that will be available to you before the public.
metadata.name: Rap Pack RillaVerse [Gorilla Mansion Inspired]
